{"tid":1631534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實各地開花贏嘅係各地roadblock","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:07:24.000Z","uid":43668,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f6e9c0e5683bd7ede49b83beea7c9397dbc8309e","tid":1631534,"uid":43668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"啲黑警比啲roadblock block行動力幾乎=0<br />\n黨鐵又真收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />運唔到兵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而你去港島反而比機會班狗set roadblock <br />\n個分別就係係到<br />\nRoadblock應該要比手足set 仲要set到全港都係<br />\n咁班狗=廢左"},{"pid":"2783c23a2f8c2250328a26898c2a588e1aa33cf1","tid":1631534,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"0f38d55552ee17208348a48d571a44cc997ba893","tid":1631534,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"公安行呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「極重要」《三份英國外交及國會報告》：當代及後世香港抗爭者之啟示</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"666e08c0440fa3046648ea21278cff8b6385eba7","tid":1631534,"uid":180470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:36.000Z","msg":"I support"},{"pid":"d9850a76ff07afed93bad8a57ec43efd113f7660","tid":1631534,"uid":180470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:46.000Z","msg":"I help you"},{"pid":"2bbb94dc80f798cb5210ee939d4d324a3f64ef63","tid":1631534,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:48:17.000Z","msg":"支持，個重心可以擺返响塞交通度"},{"pid":"d416a75873f08003fb4e53b23524d9b6b0c430c0","tid":1631534,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:04.000Z","msg":"其實有D似我個po入面講烏克蘭人嘅經歷wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631278</a>"},{"pid":"f28d6de064e16900f3d407d0da4b5d17c1ea06b8","tid":1631534,"uid":166853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb461ae0f6af43fe3c14624612cfae7566e5ba46","tid":1631534,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:43.000Z","msg":"聽日一撚定要夜晚18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br /